Author: BladderPatrol
Text: Oh yea all the time! But I used to work around food and smelling was a big part of the job. Now I just take deep whiffs of everything reflexively

Author: my-destructive-side
Text: Not just my own food, but other people’s food as well. (I mean, not random strangers or anything, but I’ve def asked family/friends/coworkers if I could smell their food. I’m a fucking weirdo.)
